Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Contra aid cut off
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xksz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 May 1985
Defeat for the president as House cuts off aid to Nicaragua's Contras amid fears of another Vietnam. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less